99-0603 (La. 4/23/99)

Wendell CLEMENT, et al. v. AMERICAN MOTORIST INSURANCE COMPANY, et al. No. 99-C-0603. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: American Dynasty Surp. Lines; — Defendant(s); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs; Parish of Calcasieu 14th Judicial District Court Div. “E” Number 95-223; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, Number CW98-0504

Denied.

CALOGERO, C.J. not on panel. MARCUS and VICTORY, JJ. would grant the writ.
